# Normalise line endings so the working tree stops showing every file as
# modified on Windows/WSL checkouts. The index already stores LF; declaring
# `text=auto eol=lf` makes Git normalise on comparison, so no content rewrite
# is needed. Batch files keep CRLF — cmd.exe can mis-parse LF-only labels.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.bat text eol=crlf

*.svg text eol=lf

*.png binary
*.ico binary
